scripts.praktikum_c: sh -c '[ -z "$npm_config_modul" ] && echo "Error: Parameter --modul (modul) dibutuhkan!" && exit 1; [ -z "$npm_config_file" ] && echo "Error: Parameter --file (file) dibutuhkan!" && exit 1; mkdir -p ./praktikum/$npm_config_modul/build && g++ ./praktikum/$npm_config_modul/app/$npm_config_file.cross -o ./praktikum/$npm_config_modul/build/$npm_config_file.exe; ./praktikum/$npm_config_modul/build/$npm_config_file.exe'
scripts.praktikum_cpp: sh -c '[ -z "$npm_config_modul" ] && echo "Error: Parameter --modul (modul) dibutuhkan!" && exit 1; [ -z "$npm_config_file" ] && echo "Error: Parameter --file (file) dibutuhkan!" && exit 1; mkdir -p ./praktikum/$npm_config_modul/build && g++ ./praktikum/$npm_config_modul/app/$npm_config_file.cpp -o ./praktikum/$npm_config_modul/build/$npm_config_file.exe; ./praktikum/$npm_config_modul/build/$npm_config_file.exe'
